metadata.name: BEAR MACHINE//BMATM-0A1B2C3D-CP #1/20
metadata.description: A digital art piece that features a rendering of an ATM machine of  bear market. The machine has been carefully modelled and textured using computer software, resulting in an authentic and visually stunning artwork. The attention to detail and skillful use of digital tools make this piece a unique and impressive creation. It is clear that you have a strong understanding of computer graphics and a talent for creating digital art. This piece is sure to be enjoyed by anyone who appreciates innovative and creative digital artworks.
